                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Mengidentifikasi keterkaitan setiap mata pelajaran dengan kehidupan nyata agar peserta didik melihat relevansi pembelajaran</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-primary-50/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-primary-100">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Mengidentifikasi potensi mata pelajaran terhadap pencapaian <strong class="text-primary-600">8 Dimensi Profil Lulusan</strong></p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-primary-50/50 p-5 rounded-xl border border-primary-100">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Memilih strategi pembelajaran yang mendorong murid merancang proyek, melakukan penelitian, atau menyelesaikan tantangan berbasis data sesuai mata pelajaran</p>
